@startuml System_Layers_Simple
!theme plain

skinparam defaultFontSize 20
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam packageBorderThickness 4

title <size:28><b>System Layers</b></size>

package "<size:24><b>WEB INTERFACE</b></size>" #F8BBD0 {
    [<size:20><b>React Dashboard</b></size>\n<size:16>Mission Planning\nLive Monitoring\nData Visualization</size>]
}

package "<size:24><b>APPLICATION</b></size>" #FFF9C4 {
    [<size:20><b>FastAPI Backend</b></size>\n<size:16>REST API\nData Storage\nMission Control</size>]
}

package "<size:24><b>ROBOT CONTROL</b></size>" #BBDEFB {
    [<size:20><b>ROS Navigation</b></size>\n<size:16>Waypoint Planning\nObstacle Detection\nMotor Control</size>]
}

package "<size:24><b>HARDWARE</b></size>" #FFCCBC {
    [<size:20><b>Sensors & Actuators</b></size>\n<size:16>Lidar • Camera\nThermal • Motors</size>]
}

[React Dashboard] -down-> [FastAPI Backend] : <size:18><b>HTTP/REST</b></size>
[FastAPI Backend] -down-> [ROS Navigation] : <size:18><b>ROS Topics</b></size>
[ROS Navigation] -down-> [Sensors & Actuators] : <size:18><b>Direct I/O</b></size>

note right of [React Dashboard]
    <size:16><b>User Control</b></size>
    <size:14>• Configure missions
    • Monitor progress
    • View results</size>
end note

note right of [ROS Navigation]
    <size:16><b>Autonomous</b></size>
    <size:14>• No manual driving
    • Auto obstacle avoid
    • Complete coverage</size>
end note

@enduml
